<p>英 /ɡʌn/    美 /ɡʌn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>枪；炮；手枪：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>machine gun</strong>
机关枪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fire</strong> a<strong> gun</strong> at sb
向某人开枪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When guns speak it is too late to argue.
待到炮声响，辩论已莫及。</p></div></div>